title: Little Devil Teemo Icon Not Received ?
body:
Haven't received the icon after winning a game last week and one a few days ago proof links above ^_^ (Is this how you earn it orrrrr?)

Match History Win Links: http://matchhistory.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/#match-details/NA1/2324070063/219908129?tab=overview     http://matchhistory.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/#match-details/NA1/2331829863/219908129?tab=overview

replies.body: Yup, those are the right games modes. We're sending these icons out over time and you should receive yours by no later than November 17th. If you don't have it by then, you can submit a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) and we'll help you out.
